node.text:
Do you you agree?👀 Your social media's feed says more about you then what's currently happening in the world. Part of the reason why you keep seeing negative news on your feed is because you keep interacting with those type of content. And the algorithm takes note of your behavior to keep feeding you content that you are likely to interact with...

Anyway, this is a snippet of an hour long interview I did with @startcanadapodcast 2 weeks ago where we talked about social media marketing for entrepreneurs.

Go check out their page @startcanadapodcast 👈to see the full episode if you want some free tips on growing your business utilizing social media as a tool. 📲

⁣
You’ve got some stuff to offer the world my friend – and there are people willing to pay you for teaching it to them. And don’t worry if you can’t figure out what that is right now… we’ll help with that too!⁣

⁣
Reserve your spot now before it's too late‼ Click the link in my bio @iamdaviddang 👈⁣ to claim your FREE spot for the Own Your Future Challenge 📲

What if it was possible to change the course of your life with just ONE decision…

No money needed, no special experience, just 5 days (90 minutes a day) and a simple commitment…

Would you do it??

On May 11th, the Own Your Future Challenge begins…

For five days, 17 world-changers I admire so much including Tony Robbins, Dean Graziosi, Russell Brunson, Prince E.A. plus many other thought leaders will be sharing the secrets to turning what’s ALREADY inside your head into real, measurable success and impact.

I’ll be there and this is your chance to join for free…

👉 Go to the link in my bio @iamdaviddang to register for this FREE event now!🔥

Or type in www.ownit63.com in your web browser to claim your spot before it's over!📲

node.text:
You are missing out by not sharing your knowledge to others. ⠀
⠀
Because most people are totally unaware of the value of their own knowledge and skills, and are unsure how to share what they know to others. ⠀
⠀
I’m willing to bet you didn’t know that the “self education” industry is exploding right now and projected by Forbes to TRIPLE in the next 5 years (most people don’t)...⠀
⠀
👉📲 🔗🔗Go to the link in my bio now @iamdaviddang if you'd like to take advantage of this!🔗🔗📲👈⠀
⠀
AND I’d bet even more that you don’t think it applies to you. ⠀
⠀
Here’s why you’re wrong:⠀
⠀
Whether you realize it or not, you have expertise, skills, hobbies, heck knowledge that people in the world want and need. You might not know what that is, but I’m telling you, YOU DO. ⠀
That’s where the “self education” industry comes in. People are willing to compensate experts for their knowledge, (I’ll repeat: experts like YOU)...⠀
⠀
So imagine this - what if you could harness that specialized knowledge you have and share it with the world…
⠀
And what if by doing that, you made an impact on peoples’ lives AND achieved the personal success you crave from it? ⠀
⠀
You may not realize it… but I’m impacting lives and making income myself as part of the “self education”industry. Crazy that this was so hidden before, right?!?⠀
⠀
Guess what!⠀
⠀
Dean Graziosi and Tony Robbins is doing a FREE 5 day Own Your Future Challenge to take back control of your career and future as the world is opening up again. You can use it to figure out what knowledge you have, learn how you could share it and get paid for it… so basically what I’m saying is...⠀
⠀
Welcome to your new life of sharing ;-)⠀
⠀
The free challenge begins on May 11th. Don’t miss this! Those average, “meh” filled days will be over if you decide right now to end them!⠀
⠀
👉📲 🔗🔗 CLICK THE LINK IN MY BIO @IAMDAVIDDANG TO REGISTER🔗🔗📲👈⠀
⠀
Or you can type in www.ownit63.com in your web browser to claim your spot before it's too late!👨‍💻

node.text:
If you’re serious about becoming successful, keep reading.

So, you want to finally discover how to be successful?

First, imagine where you’ll honestly be in the next five years.

Maybe on a beach, working remote while drinking your favorite cocktail or beer. Or maybe you’ll be sitting on a couch, watching Netflix, and still dreaming.

Your success lies in your hands.

I could tell you all the things you need to do to be successful, and at first you’ll probably do a couple of those things, but six months from now you’ll be back to your current routine.

So, do you want to finally figure out how to be successful and do it. Or do you want to keep dreaming about it?

Most people obsess over how to be successful because we all want to feel like we matter.

Without achieving any success, we might look back on our life disappointed by our lack of impact on the world.

Striving to achieve a greater purpose is what keeps us fighting to survive and grow.

While you might not become an international success, your life can still have an impact on others.

The goal of achieving success will help you live a more purposeful life by pushing you to overcome obstacles, work a bit harder and pursue happiness.

As a result, I strongly advise you to follow some of the best mentors on Instagram today.
Their regular Instagram updates and posts will assist you in achieving your goals. They are as follows:

If you’re serious about changing your life forever, keep reading.

The number one way to get ahead in life is to learn a new skill. The more skills you obtain, the more successful you will be. 

Did you know that on average it only takes about 6 months to obtain a new skill that could change your life forever?

So then why is it that most people never learn new skills or educate themselves?

The answer is simple. They lack the discipline. They’d rather stay comfortable and spend their spare time relaxing instead of using it to DISAPPEAR to learn and improve.

But not you, you’re different. You recognize the value of your time and are hungry to improve.

By chasing success and improvement, you will live a more purposeful and meaningful life, a life that others only dream of.

For that reason, I personally recommend you follow these accounts who are helping people level up in every aspect of life. Their usernames are as follows:

Your 2030 lifestyle will be determined by your 2021 decisions.⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣
⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣
The most important thing you can do to make sure your 2030 lifestyle will be exactly, if not better, than what you want is to be BUILDING:⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣
⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣
Building Your Business. Your Body. Your health. Your self-esteem. Your bank account. ⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣
⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣
The problem is... By 2030 most people reading this WILL NOT build anything significant for themselves and their families.⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣
⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣
Why?⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣
⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣

⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣
Our current education system doesn't teach us how to build the future we really want.⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣
⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣
We learn different topics that will help us have great 9-5 or different careers... That in fact won't help us build the future we REALLY want.⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣
